## Key Nomenclature

- **%DAU/WAU/MAU**: Percentage of Daily/Weekly/Monthly Active Users performing an event
- **Average Times Performed**: The average number of times users perform an event in the selected time period
- **Average Days Performed**: The average number of days users perform an event in the selected time period
- **Breadth**: The horizontal axis measuring the percentage of active users performing an event
- **Frequency**: The vertical axis measuring how often users perform an event
- **Data Point Clusters**: Groups of events with similar engagement patterns